40:58.600 --> 41:03.160
equals one. So, this is all just to say that a completely

41:03.160 --> 41:07.240
general su2 matrix can be given by four real numbers

41:07.240 --> 41:11.880
x, y, z, and w such that x squared plus y squared plus z squared plus w

41:11.880 --> 41:16.440
squared equals one. This is the equation for something called

41:16.440 --> 41:21.320
the three sphere, which we denote s3.

41:27.320 --> 41:32.120
How do we picture this three sphere? Well, you might be familiar with the two

